## 8. 蜂鸣器

### 8A. 板载蜂鸣器（M10背面）

```python
from pinpong.extension.unihiker import *
Board().begin()
buzzer.play(buzzer.DADADADUM, buzzer.Once)
buzzer.pitch(440, 4)  # 440Hz, 4拍
```

预置音乐：`DADADADUM`, `ENTERTAINER`, `PRELUDE`, `ODE`, `NYAN`, `RINGTONE`, `FUNK`, `BLUES`, `BIRTHDAY`, `WEDDING`

### 8B. 外接有源蜂鸣器模块
**DFRobot 型号：DFR0032**

